text: Lenka Zavadilová (born 7 July 1975) is a Czech rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. Her brother Radek Zavadil is also an Olympic rower. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Czech female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Prague
